import Button from "./component/inputs/button/Button"
import styled, {ThemeProvider} from "styled-components"
import Icon from "./component/icon/Icon"
const ButtonWrapper = styled.div`
    width: 360px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
`
const theme={
    primary : '#5C7CFA'
}

function App () {
    return(
        <ThemeProvider theme={theme}>
            <ButtonWrapper>
                <Button size="large">버어튼</Button>
                <Button>버어튼</Button>
                <Button size="small">버어튼</Button>
            </ButtonWrapper>
            <ButtonWrapper>
                <Button color="warnning">버어튼</Button>
                <Button >버어튼</Button>
                <Button color="mono">버어튼</Button>
                <Button disabled>버어튼</Button>
            </ButtonWrapper>
            <ButtonWrapper>
                <Button color="warnning" outline>버어튼</Button>
                <Button outline>버어튼</Button>
                <Button disabled outline>버어튼</Button>
            </ButtonWrapper>
            <ButtonWrapper>
                <Button shape="square">버어튼</Button>
                <Button>버어튼</Button>
                <Button shape="pill">버어튼</Button>
            </ButtonWrapper>
            <ButtonWrapper>
                <Button fullWidth>버어튼</Button>
                <Button shape="square" fullWidth>버어튼</Button>
                <Button shape="square" fullWidth color="mono">확인</Button>
            </ButtonWrapper>
            <Icon width="16" height="16" color="red"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M8.272 4.9526C7.174 4.9526 6.077 5.3496 5.241 6.1446C4.441 6.9066 4 7.9176 4 8.9916C4 10.0646 4.441 11.0756 5.241 11.8376L12 18.2696L18.759 11.8376C19.559 11.0756 20 10.0646 20 8.9916C20 7.9186 19.559 6.9066 18.759 6.1446C17.088 4.5546 14.368 4.5546 12.697 6.1446L12 6.8086L11.303 6.1446C10.467 5.3496 9.37 4.9526 8.272 4.9526ZM12 20.9996L3.847 13.2406C2.656 12.1076 2 10.5986 2 8.9916C2 7.3846 2.656 5.8756 3.847 4.7416C6.067 2.6286 9.552 2.4386 12 4.1686C14.448 2.4386 17.933 2.6286 20.153 4.7416C21.344 5.8756 22 7.3846 22 8.9916C22 10.5986 21.344 12.1076 20.153 13.2406L12 20.9996Z"/></Icon>
        </ThemeProvider>
    )
}

export default App
